title: [New Team Member] - Business Development & Strategy
body:
We are happy to have Blakeburrito as our new team member who will help move inSure DeFi to the next level by using his vast knowledge of the crypto world and establishing new business partnerships with other projects and influencers.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/blakeburrito
Gitcoin: https://gitcoin.co/blakeburrito

In order to incentivize the efforts of our new member, we are asking inSure DAO to approve the first stake transfer of 100 000 SURE to the wallet of BlakeBurrito (0x6E9A88971e957Abb41bAe4E2677caE258F0c1e76).

Once this ticket is approved by inSure DAO the funds will be transferred from inSure DeFi Platform's wallet.
